<capabilities>
Equipped with a variety of tools these platoons engage in some of the most dangerous tasks assigned to combat engineers - explosive ordnance disposal, clearing minefields, and explosive demolition of obstacles and buildings. As such they are equipped with much heavier protective gear than normally found among infantry.
